title: Are These VHS Tapes ‘Rare’ and Worth Big Money?
subtitle: An advertised list reported that first-release VHS tapes of "Barney: Waiting for Santa," "Halloween," "Star Wars," and others were rare and worth good money.
author: Jordan Liles
vclaim: A list shows a handful of rare VHS movies and specials that can land a nice sum for owners — potentially even hundreds or thousands of dollars.
